description: PARKING....ROOF DECK....PENTHOUSE....This two bedroom condo has an open floor plan which is perfect for entertaining. The sleek kitchen has granite and stainless. This condo offers all the modern amenities including: 2 gas fireplaces, tub, hardwood floors throughout, high ceilings, central AC, in unit washer/dryer, storage, lots of natural sunlight, 2 decks ( including a roof deck). and a deeded parking spot. Available September 1, 2019
